    {
      "text": "R.B.I. Baseball is a baseball sports video game series. R.B.I. stands for \"runs batted in\". Launched in 1987 as a localized version of Namco's Family Stadium series, the R.B.I. Baseball series initially ran through 1995. In 2014, the series was rebooted as a competitor to MLB: The Show, with releases each year until its cancellation. The series continued until 2021.",
